{
  "stem": "4670.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the terrible thing was not just the pictures, but the voice of Goering was screaming.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I came home, I was destroyed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I was-- it was awful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It was just awful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I was a teenager.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It was a difficult, difficult time for me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And my father luckily recognized it was a crucial time in my life.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Papi sat me down and said to me, look, this is not new.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "This has existed for centuries.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Jews have always been a minority, and minorities such as us have suffered.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But we will not die, we will prevail.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But you must remember, we're the people of the book.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We believe in education.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We believe in ethics.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "These are our laws.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "So long as you hold on to that, you'll be fine.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I don't think I ever forgot that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And this is something that became really my backbone for all those years.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "But it's pretty bad for a kid to grow up to have no identity.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] After that-- this was 1936-- things got worse practically daily.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "We contacted our family in the United States and they finally said to come.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And it took us a long time, but we finally got our visas.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Now--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I decided-- I didn't really-- they didn't really ever come out and tell me-- but I decided I think the reason they did that is because they were afraid they had to support us.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My grandmother's sister and brother, who became our wonderful family when I came here, had visited us in 1928.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
